data.description: Welcome to your turn key dream home on the well known Foulk Road, situated in the highly sought-after 19803 zip code of North Wilmington. This exquisite split-level house boasts four bedrooms, two and a half bathrooms, and has been meticulously fully updated with modern finishes throughout.  Step inside to discover a spacious living area with gleaming hardwood floors and abundant natural light. The open-concept layout seamlessly connects the living room to the dining area and gourmet kitchen, featuring beautiful countertops and stainless steel appliances. Retreat to the primary bedroom suite offering a luxurious en suite bathroom, while three additional bedrooms offer versatility. Outside, the private backyard oasis is perfect for entertaining or relaxation. With its prime location near shopping, dining, parks, and schools, this home combines comfort, style, and convenience in one desirable package. Don't miss out—schedule your showing today to experience the best of North Wilmington living!
